In the file "tasks.json" for first tutorials with the text:

{
    // See https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=733558
    // for the documentation about the tasks.json format
    "version": "2.0.0",
    "command": "tsc",
    "isShellCommand":true,
    "args": ["-w","-p","."],
    "showOutput": "silent",
    "isWatching": true,
    "problemMatcher": "$tsc-watch"   
}

these lines are underlined:
"isShellCommand":true,
 "showOutput": "silent",
    "isWatching": true,
    
with the following problem: "The property showOutput (and so on) is deprecated. 
Use the reveal property inside the presentation property instead. See also the 1.14 release notes."
